# iMessage plain text only

Outbound chat text (interaction agent, computer result summaries, delivery copy) is plain iMessage text.

- Never use Markdown bold/italics: no `**word**`, `*word*`, or `_word_`.
- Wrong: `The answer was **CHURN**, solved in **4 guesses**.`
- Right: `The answer was CHURN, solved in 4 guesses.`
- Keep prompt rules explicit about this; strip Markdown emphasis in delivery helpers when model output may still include it.
